<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Roya · Documents</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: #f8fafc;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .nav {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 24px 32px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            background: white;
        }

        .logo {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 26px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1b4b, #4f46e5);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: #334155;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #4f46e5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 32px;
        }

        /* Header */
        .page-header {
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .page-header h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .lead {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #475569;
        }

        /* Document Tabs / Navigation */
        .doc-tabs {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .tab-link {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            color: #475569;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .tab-link:hover,
        .tab-link.active {
            background: #eef2ff;
            border-color: #4f46e5;
            color: #4f46e5;
        }

        /* Document Sections */
        .doc-section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            scroll-margin-top: 80px;
        }

        .doc-section h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .doc-section h2 i {
            color: #4f46e5;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .section-meta {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        /* Two Column Layout (for What We Store) */
        .storage-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .storage-box {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 28px;
        }

        .storage-box.blockchain {
            background: #0f172a;
            color: white;
        }

        .storage-box h3 {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .checklist {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .checklist li {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .check-yes {
            color: #10b981;
            width: 24px;
        }

        .check-no {
            color: #ef4444;
            width: 24px;
        }

        /* Table Styles */
        .table-container {
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        th {
            background: #eef2ff;
            padding: 16px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        td {
            padding: 16px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .check-yes-table {
            color: #10b981;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .check-no-table {
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        .footnote {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* Contact Box */
        .contact-box {
            background: #eef2ff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 32px;
            margin: 48px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .contact-box a {
            background: white;
            color: #4f46e5;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #c7d2fe;
        }

        .footer {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 32px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
            color: #64748b;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #334155;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            color: #4f46e5;
        }

        /* Site color scheme overrides (matches landing page) */
        :root {
            --bg-main: #0a0a0a;
            --bg-elev: #111111;
            --bg-soft: #151515;
            --text-main: #e0e0e0;
            --text-dim: #9ca3af;
            --line: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.25);
            --accent: #22d3ee;
            --accent-2: #22d3ee;
        }

        body {
            background: var(--bg-main);
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .nav {
            background: #000000;
            border-bottom-color: var(--line);
        }

        .logo {
            background: none;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: var(--accent);
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .nav-links a,
        .lead,
        .section-meta,
        td,
        .footnote,
        .footer,
        .footer a {
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover,
        .tab-link:hover,
        .tab-link.active,
        .doc-section h2 i,
        .contact-box a {
            color: var(--accent-2);
        }

        .tab-link,
        .doc-section,
        .table-container table,
        .contact-box,
        .footer,
        .storage-box,
        .compliance-item,
        .access-table-wrap,
        .footnote,
        .contact-block {
            background: var(--bg-elev);
            border-color: var(--line);
        }

        .storage-box,
        th,
        .doc-tabs,
        .tab-link {
            background: var(--bg-soft);
            border-color: var(--line);
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .doc-section h2,
        .storage-box h3,
        .principle-card h3,
        .compliance-item h4,
        th,
        .page-header h1 {
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .page-header h1 {
            background: none;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: initial;
        }

        .contact-box a {
            background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.45);
        }

        .doc-section,
        .principle-card,
        .compliance-item,
        .storage-box,
        .access-table-wrap,
        .contact-box {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover,
        .footer a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-2);
        }

        .contact-box a:hover {
            background: #22d3ee;
            color: #000000;
            border-color: transparent;
        }

        [style*="background: #f1f5f9"],
        [style*="background:#f1f5f9"],
        [style*="background: #f8fafc"],
        [style*="background:#f8fafc"],
        [style*="background: #ffffff"],
        [style*="background:#ffffff"],
        [style*="background: white"],
        [style*="background:white"] {
            background: var(--bg-soft) !important;
            border: 1px solid var(--line) !important;
            color: var(--text-main) !important;
        }

        [style*="color: #334155"],
        [style*="color:#334155"],
        [style*="color: #475569"],
        [style*="color:#475569"],
        [style*="color: #64748b"],
        [style*="color:#64748b"],
        [style*="color: #0f172a"],
        [style*="color:#0f172a"] {
            color: var(--text-dim) !important;
        }

        [style*="color: #10b981"],
        [style*="color:#10b981"],
        [style*="color: #4f46e5"],
        [style*="color:#4f46e5"],
        [style*="color: #a5b4fc"],
        [style*="color:#a5b4fc"] {
            color: var(--accent) !important;
        }

        [style*="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0"],
        [style*="border:1px solid #e2e8f0"],
        [style*="border: 1px solid #c7d2fe"],
        [style*="border:1px solid #c7d2fe"] {
            border-color: var(--line) !important;
        }

        @media (max-width: 700px) {
            .storage-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="nav">
        <a href="/" class="logo">Roya</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/documents.html" style="color: #22d3ee; font-weight: 600;">Documents</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="page-header">
            <h1>Documents</h1>
            <p class="lead">All Roya policies, guides, and legal information in one place.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick Navigation Tabs -->
        <div class="doc-tabs">
            <a href="#terms" class="tab-link">📄 Terms</a>
            <a href="#privacy-security" class="tab-link">🔒 Privacy & Security</a>
            <a href="#gdpr" class="tab-link">🇪🇺 GDPR</a>
            <a href="#how-it-works" class="tab-link">⚙️ How It Works</a>
            <a href="#what-we-store" class="tab-link">📦 What We Store</a>
            <a href="#security" class="tab-link">🛡️ Security</a>
            <a href="#dispute" class="tab-link">⚖️ Dispute</a>
        </div>

        <!-- 1. TERMS OF SERVICE -->
        <section id="terms" class="doc-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i> Terms of Service</h2>
            <div class="section-meta">
                <span><i class="fas fa-calendar"></i> Last updated: 15 Feb 2026 · v2.1</span>
                <span><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Swedish law</span>
            </div>
            <div style="max-height: 400px; overflow-y: auto; padding-right: 16px;">
                <h3>1. Definitions</h3>
                <p>"Roya" refers to Roya AB, a Swedish company. "Service" means the Roya verification platform. "Publisher" means the entity using the Service.</p>
                
                <h3>2. Eligibility</h3>
                <p>You must be at least 18 years old and have authority to bind your organization.</p>
                
                <h3>3. Verification Service</h3>
                <p>Roya provides a cryptographic verification layer for music publishing splits. We store only hashes on-chain; all personal data remains with you.</p>
                
                <h3>4. Data Ownership</h3>
                <p>You retain full ownership of all split sheets. Roya claims no intellectual property over your content.</p>
                
                <h3>5. Acceptable Use</h3>
                <p>You agree not to use the Service for illegal purposes or to infringe third-party rights.</p>
                
                <h3>6. Fees</h3>
                <p>Currently free during testnet evaluation. Future fees will be announced with 30 days notice.</p>
                
                <h3>7. Limitation of Liability</h3>
                <p>The Service is provided "AS IS". Roya's total liability is limited to €50 for free users.</p>
                
                <h3>8. Governing Law</h3>
                <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of Sweden. Disputes shall be resolved in Stockholm courts.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. PRIVACY & SECURITY (Your Full Content) -->
        <section id="privacy-security" class="doc-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Privacy & Security</h2>
            <div class="section-meta">
                <span><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> GDPR compliant · by design, by default</span>
            </div>
            
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 32px;">Roya is built with privacy-first architecture that separates verification proof from personal data.</p>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                <div style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 16px;">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-chart-line" style="color: #4f46e5;"></i> Data minimisation</h4>
                    <p style="color: #334155;">Only verification metadata is stored; all personal data remains with publishers.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 16px;">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-trash-alt" style="color: #4f46e5;"></i> Right to erasure (Art. 17)</h4>
                    <p style="color: #334155;">Publishers can delete contributor data; anonymous proof remains as audit trail.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 16px;">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-user-tie" style="color: #4f46e5;"></i> Data controller</h4>
                    <p style="color: #334155;">Publishers remain controller. Roya acts as processor for verification only.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 16px;">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-bullseye" style="color: #4f46e5;"></i> Purpose limitation</h4>
                    <p style="color: #334155;">Data used solely for split verification, not marketing or other purposes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 style="margin: 40px 0 20px;">What we store (and where)</h3>
            
            <div class="storage-grid">
                <!-- Blockchain column -->
                <div class="storage-box blockchain">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-cube"></i> Blockchain (Monad testnet)</h3>
                    <ul class="checklist">
                        <li><span class="check-yes"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></span> Verification timestamp</li>
                        <li><span class="check-yes"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></span> Content hash (cryptographic fingerprint)</li>
                        <li><span class="check-yes"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></span> Basic statistics (contributor count, total %)</li>
                        <li style="opacity: 0.6;"><span class="check-no"><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i></span> NO personal information</li>
                        <li style="opacity: 0.6;"><span class="check-no"><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i></span> NO names or payment details</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #a5b4fc;"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> public but anonymous</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Your systems column -->
                <div class="storage-box" style="background: #f1f5f9;">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-server"></i> Your systems (your control)</h3>
                    <ul class="checklist">
                        <li><span style="color: #10b981;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></span> All contributor details</li>
                        <li><span style="color: #10b981;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></span> Split percentages per person</li>
                        <li><span style="color: #10b981;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></span> Payment calculations</li>
                        <li><span style="color: #10b981;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></span> Under your complete control</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #475569;"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> never shared with Roya</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 style="margin: 40px 0 20px;">🇪🇺 GDPR compliance built‑in</h3>
            
            <div style="background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px; margin-bottom: 32px;">
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;">
                    <div>
                        <strong>Data minimization</strong><br>
                        <span style="color: #475569;">Only verification metadata stored</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Right to erasure</strong><br>
                        <span style="color: #475569;">Delete contributor data, keep proof</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Data controller</strong><br>
                        <span style="color: #475569;">Publishers control, Roya processes</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Purpose limitation</strong><br>
                        <span style="color: #475569;">Verification only, no marketing</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Secure processing</strong><br>
                        <span style="color: #475569;">Isolated, encrypted environments</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 style="margin: 40px 0 20px;">Audit trail · without privacy risk</h3>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px; margin-bottom: 32px;">
                <div style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 24px; border-radius: 16px;">
                    <h4 style="color: #10b981; margin-bottom: 16px;">✓ The blockchain proves:</h4>
                    <ul style="list-style: none;">
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: #10b981;"></i> A split was verified</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: #10b981;"></i> At a specific time</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: #10b981;"></i> With specific characteristics (4 people, 100% total)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 24px; border-radius: 16px;">
                    <h4 style="color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 16px;">❌ But reveals nothing about:</h4>
                    <ul style="list-style: none;">
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-ban" style="color: #94a3b8;"></i> Who the contributors are</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-ban" style="color: #94a3b8;"></i> How much they're receiving</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-ban" style="color: #94a3b8;"></i> Which work this relates to</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 40px;">✅ This allows independent verification without compromising privacy.</p>

            <h3 style="margin: 40px 0 20px;">Access control – who can see what</h3>
            
            <div class="table-container">
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Data type</th>
                            <th>Publishers</th>
                            <th>PRO*</th>
                            <th>Roya</th>
                            <th>Public</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td>Contributor names</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓*</td><td class="check-no-table">❌</td><td class="check-no-table">❌</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Split percentages</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓*</td><td class="check-no-table">❌</td><td class="check-no-table">❌</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Payment amounts</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td><td class="check-no-table">❌</td><td class="check-no-table">❌</td><td class="check-no-table">❌</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Verification timestamp</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td></tr>
                        <tr><td>Content hash</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td><td class="check-yes-table">✓</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <p class="footnote">* Only when publisher submits registration to PRO through normal process. PRO does not have direct access to Roya data. The table indicates what could be shared during standard royalty reporting.</p>

            <h3 style="margin: 40px 0 20px;">Secure processing & isolation</h3>
            <p style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 16px;">All verification happens in isolated, encrypted environments. No data shared between publishers. Every tenant isolated.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. GDPR COMPLIANCE -->
        <section id="gdpr" class="doc-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i> GDPR Compliance</h2>
            <div class="section-meta">
                <span><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Articles 5, 17, 24, 28</span>
            </div>
            <p>Roya is designed to help publishers meet their GDPR obligations. Key principles:</p>
            <ul style="margin: 20px 0 20px 20px;">
                <li><strong>Article 5:</strong> Data minimization – only hashes stored</li>
                <li><strong>Article 17:</strong> Right to erasure – delete personal data, keep proof</li>
                <li><strong>Article 24:</strong> Controller responsibility – you control data</li>
                <li><strong>Article 28:</strong> Processor obligations – Roya acts as processor</li>
            </ul>
            <p>For full details, see <a href="#privacy-security" style="color: #4f46e5;">Privacy & Security</a> section above.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- 4. HOW VERIFICATION WORKS -->
        <section id="how-it-works" class="doc-section">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> How Verification Works</h2>
            <div class="section-meta">
                <span><i class="fas fa-cube"></i> Monad testnet · Digital notary stamp</span>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px; margin-bottom: 32px; text-align: center;">
                <i class="fas fa-certificate" style="font-size: 48px; color: #4f46e5; margin-bottom: 16px;"></i>
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Digital Notary Stamp</h3>
                <p style="color: #475569;">The blockchain stores only a mathematical proof—like a digital notary stamp. All sensitive data stays with you.</p>
            </div>

            <h4 style="margin: 32px 0 16px;">In a dispute:</h4>
            
            <div style="background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px;">
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                    <span style="background: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 4px 16px; border-radius: 40px; font-weight: 600;">You</span>
                    <span>"We verified this split on February 15, 2026"</span>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                    <span style="background: #e4e4e7; padding: 4px 16px; border-radius: 40px; font-weight: 600;">Other</span>
                    <span>"No you didn't, we never agreed"</span>
                </div>
